B.Gv=s(["Dantrolene","Baclofen","Tizanidine","Diazepam"],t.s)
B.Nt=new A.aD("Which medication is considered first-line oral treatment for generalized post-stroke spasticity?",B.Gv,1,"Baclofen (a GABA-B agonist) is typically considered first-line for generalized spasticity. Tizanidine (alpha-2 agonist) is an alternative. Dantrolene acts peripherally on muscle. Diazepam is effective but limited by sedation and dependence.")
