B.NZ=new A.aD("Botulinum toxin injection for focal spasticity works by which mechanism?",B.Id,0,"Botulinum toxin cleaves SNARE proteins required for acetylcholine vesicle fusion at the presynaptic terminal of the neuromuscular junction, causing chemical denervation and focal reduction of muscle tone.")
