B.Ii=s(["Aspirin alone","Intermittent pneumatic compression devices","Elastic compression stockings","Early weight-bearing only"],t.s)
B.NT=new A.aD("Which DVT prophylaxis method is recommended for immobilized acute ischemic stroke patients?",B.Ii,1,"Intermittent pneumatic compression (IPC) devices are recommended for DVT prophylaxis in immobilized acute stroke patients. The CLOTS 3 trial demonstrated their efficacy. Subcutaneous heparin/LMWH may be used but increases bleeding risk. Elastic stockings are NOT recommended (CLOTS 1 and 2 trials).")
