o=A.aS("Thrombotic Stroke")
q=A.b2("Thrombotic stroke results from in-situ thrombus formation on a pre-existing atherosclerotic plaque within a cerebral artery. It is the most common subtype of ischemic stroke and typically affects large and medium-sized arteries.",!0)
