q=A.ag("Board Pearl: Macular Sparing",'Macular sparing in homonymous hemianopia is the hallmark of PCA (occipital cortex) stroke and distinguishes it from optic radiation lesions. The macula is "spared" because it has dual blood supply from both PCA and MCA. This is one of the most commonly tested visual deficit localization questions.')
