j=A.ag("Board Pearl: Wallenberg -- Most Tested Brainstem Syndrome","Wallenberg syndrome has NO motor weakness -- this is crucial for the exam. The corticospinal tract runs in the medial medulla and is spared in lateral medullary lesions. Key features to remember: ipsilateral face + contralateral body pain/temp loss, Horner syndrome, dysphagia, cerebellar ataxia, vertigo.")
